cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.IT 

Reasoning: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning scheme to learn the optimal handover controllers. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper deals with handover control in wireless systems supporting mobile IoT users or traditional cellular users. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a framework to control the handover processes across multiple users in a wireless system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning scheme to optimize the handover controllers. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper deals with optimizing the handover processes in a wireless system, which involves information theory concepts such as throughput and HO rate.
